name: SensiHunt
overview:
SensiHunt.com is a community created by Medical Marijuana Patients for Medical Marijuana Patients. We seek to provide the most up to date, accurate, and reliable information pertaining to Dispensaries, Delivery Services, Doctors, and Smoke Shops. Our reviews, comments, profile, friend and following system allows the community members, like you, to give individual accounts of your experiences and allows you to read other memberâ€™s feedback. This gives members unbiased, diverse, and unique critiques to better assist you in choosing where to go for your medical needs. With this feedback, businesses will know what their patients needs and concerns are, and allows them to reach out to patients and better serve them. At SensiHunt, we strive to better our community one review at a time.

Join now and be part of our growing and thriving community!
